planet_argon_recipes
==================
A rails plugin of capistrano recipes for Planet Argon's shared hosting.

This will simplify deployment on Planet Argon's by encapsulating knowledge of their hosting contraints, traps, tricks, methods, etc.



steps to setting up trouble-free deployment
============================================
1) determine the
rake rails:freeze:gems #freeze rails version in vendor
add 'config.gem' lines for all require gems in environment.rb
rake gems:unpack:dependencies  #freezes all required gems
capify .





Example
=======
:pa_planet

Example goes here.


